  "title": "Tapping for emotional overload at bedtime",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute night script for emptying the emotional weight of the day before sleep.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 6 of Rebecca's SLEEP program. The script targets the accumulated emotional weight of the day, the feelings that haven't been processed, sitting in the body at bedtime.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from the Night Tap on Day 6 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Ease Emotional Overload.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
